Concepts
-Meant to treat components the same whether it is a part of a structure or a while structure
-Individual objects treated as a composite
-Same operations applied on individual composites

Examples:
    -jwt.Component
    -JSF Widgets
    -RESTful Service GETs

Design
-Tree structured where the root is the component.
-Components are a lead or a composite of objects
-Leaf or composite, same operations
-Composite knows about child objects
-Component, Leaf, Composite

UML
-Component is the abstract for all components
-The component can define methods for accessing the component
-The leaf implements all of the Components methods
-The composite is a component that has methods that allow the interaction with children

